ions, stellar models and magnetic fields, are compared with frequencies\nof observed quasi-periodic oscillations (QPOS) in SGR 1806-20 and SGR1900+14.\nAs in earlier studies, this comparison indicates that GME modes are essential\nto explain all the frequencies as CME modes can explain only the higher\nfrequencies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2016 16:16:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
