ude-based $QED\\otimes QCD$ resummation paradigm.\nIndependently of this latter observation, the MC rigorously quantifies\nimportant EW effects in the current LHC experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2016 17:26:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2016 20:21:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
