entification: a single\ndegree-of-freedom bilinear hysteretic oscillator and a three-story shear\nbuilding with Masing hysteresis, both of which are subject to a seismic\nexcitation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2016 08:11:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-05"}
